Shree Hindu Lakhara Samaj News Website
1. 📌 Product Overview

Product Name: Shree Hindu Lakhara Samaj Digital News Platform
Platform Type: Web Application (Future Mobile App Supported)
Target Users:

Community Members

General Visitors

Admin & Committee Members

Objective:
Create a centralized digital ecosystem for the Lakhara Samaj community including news, events, directory, and social engagement.

2. 🎯 Goals & Success Metrics
Primary Goals

Community engagement increase

Digital member database creation

Event participation growth

Information transparency

KPIs

Monthly active users (MAU)

Member registrations

Event registrations

News engagement (views/shares)

Revenue from memberships/events

